      <tr><td>Drain filter clean</td><td>$89</td><td>Often free at diagnostic</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Drain pump replacement</td><td>$280 – $420</td><td>Italian-platform</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Inlet valve</td><td>$280 – $400</td><td>Fill fault</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Door hinge + alignment</td><td>$280 – $420</td><td>Panel / stainless profile variance</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Door gasket</td><td>$300 – $460</td><td>Profile-specific</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Heating element</td><td>$280 – $440</td><td>Hard-water scale</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Intelligent cycle sensor</td><td>$240 – $380</td><td>Auto-program drift</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Spray arm + jet service</td><td>$180 – $300</td><td>Premium wash architecture</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Italian specialty control board</td><td>$480 – $680</td><td>7-14 day Italian parts lead</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Circulation pump</td><td>$460 – $640</td><td>8-plus-year service</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Panel-ready trim hardware</td><td>Quoted individually</td><td>7-14 day lead</td></tr>
    </table>
    <p class="small">Related: <a href="/brands/bertazzoni-refrigerator-repair/">Bertazzoni refrigerator repair</a> · <a href="/brands/smeg-dishwasher-repair/">SMEG dishwasher repair</a> · <a href="/brands/fulgor-milano-dishwasher-repair/">Fulgor Milano dishwasher repair</a>.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>Service areas, where our Bertazzoni calls come from</h2>
    <div class="area-grid">
      <div><h4>Design-conscious eastside</h4><p>Silver Lake · Los Feliz · Highland Park · Mount Washington · Atwater Village</p></div>
      <div><h4>Westside premium</h4><p>Brentwood · Pacific Palisades · Mar Vista · <a href="/santa-monica/">Santa Monica</a></p></div>
